    "headline": "Finally a proper belting — 32-nil and the shutout tastes sweet.",
    "vibe": "First clean sheet in ages and Rinakama went absolute nuclear with 297 metres. Curran bagged a double from the bench, Burton got in on the party late, and the defence held Wests scoreless which nobody saw coming. Doesn't fix the ladder position but it buys Ciraldo another week of oxygen — and Galvin's fantasy numbers keep climbing.",
