    "kennelSummary": "Kennel's happier than it's been in weeks but nobody's getting carried away — it was the Tigers after all. Tracey still getting hammered for two out-of-position moments despite the win, and the 'fans leaving early' thread suggests even 32-0 isn't enough to keep bums on seats. Curran and Rinakama getting the flowers they deserve.",
